Company Overview
Wonderspaces is a touring exhibition of experiential art, tech, and design that makes extraordinary experiences accessible to secondary cities. Wonderspaces visits each city for three months and is open to the public for eight weeks. Guests visit Wonderspaces instead of other arts or entertainment options to share once-in-a-lifetime experiences with their friends and family.
Guests pay for admission to Wonderspaces. The physical space is an empty big-box retail store that is converted to feel like a pop-up museum. Guests will walk through a semi-directed path, where each open space contain a work of immersive art, creative technology, or design. Guests can also purchase food and visit a gift shop before they exit. They will spend roughly two hours in the space.
